ZH: 我们去露营的时候，看到了美丽的星空。
EN: When we went camping, we saw the beautiful starry sky.

ZH: 露水在早晨的草地上闪闪发光。
EN: The dew glittered on the grass in the morning.

ZH: 天气渐渐转凉，我感觉到了露寒。
EN: The weather is getting colder, I can feel the chill in the air.

ZH: 昨晚雨后，窗外的玻璃上露出了水滴。
EN: Last night after the rain, water droplets appeared on the window glass.

ZH: 他身上的汗水沁出了细细的露珠。
EN: Sweat on his body formed tiny beads of perspiration.

ZH: 露朝露露，露与露留。
EN: The dawn brings dew, dew lingers with dew.

ZH: 草地上的露珠像一颗颗小珍珠般闪闪发光。
EN: The dew on the grass glistened like tiny pearls.

ZH: 清晨的露珠让花朵显得更加美丽。
EN: The morning dew made the flowers look even more beautiful.

ZH: 在露天市场，你可以找到很多新鲜的蔬菜和水果。
EN: In the open-air market, you can find many fresh vegetables and fruits.

ZH: 露天音乐会吸引了许多音乐爱好者前来观赏。
EN: The outdoor concert attracted many music lovers to come and enjoy.

ZH: 昨晚露天电影院放映了一部经典的电影。
EN: An outdoor cinema screened a classic film last night.

ZH: 露台上的花坛里开满了五彩缤纷的花朵。
EN: The flowerbeds on the terrace are full of colorful blooms.

ZH: 我喜欢在露天游泳池里游泳，感受阳光的温暖。
EN: I enjoy swimming in the outdoor pool, feeling the warmth of the sun.

ZH: 过了露天的小桥，就是一片美丽的湖泊。
EN: Beyond the open bridge is a beautiful lake.

ZH: 他们正在露天操场上进行一场热身活动。
EN: They are warming up on the open-air playground.

ZH: 在校园里露出笑容，会让你受欢迎。
EN: Smiling in the campus will make you popular.

ZH: 入冬之际，露天露出觐今宝，小心别着凉。
EN: As winter approaches, be careful not to catch a cold in the open air.

ZH: 夜深人静时，露营的帐篷里传来欢声笑语。
EN: In the quiet of the night, laughter and joy emanate from the camping tent.

ZH: 露天市场上各种各样的商品琳琅满目。
EN: A variety of goods are on display in the open-air market.

ZH: 我们露出笑容，表示对他们的支持。
EN: We smiled to show our support for them.
